header.gameNote: Men's Basketball Championship - South Region - 1st Round

videos.headline: Jalen Slawson puts Virginia defender on a poster
videos.description: Clear the runway as Jalen Slawson soars through the paint and throws down an impressive posterizing and-1.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jalen Slawson puts Virginia defender on a poster) 2023/3/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Furman's back-to-back 3's pull them within two of Virginia
videos.description: Marcus Foster and Alex Williams knock down back-to-back triples to pull the Paladins within two.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Furman's back-to-back 3's pull them within two of Virginia) 2023/3/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jalen Slawson's and-1 gives Furman the late lead over Virginia
videos.description: Jalen Slawson is fired up as he gets the and-1 to fall for the Paladins' first lead of the game over Virginia.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jalen Slawson's and-1 gives Furman the late lead over Virginia) 2023/3/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jalen Slawson's 3 ties the game at 54 for Furman
videos.description: Jalen Slawson hits a huge 3-pointer to tie Virginia late in the game.

tracking.trackingName: **UNPUB 6/30** NCB_One-Play (Jalen Slawson’s 3 ties the game at 54 for Furman) 2023/3/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Furman's JP Pegues splashes game-winning 3 after Virginia turnover
videos.description: Kihei Clark gets trapped and turns the ball over, leading to JP Pegues 3-pointer that lifts Furman to the upset over Virginia.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Furman's JP Pegues splashes game-winning 3 after Virginia turnover) 2023/3/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Furman stuns No. 4 seed Virginia 68-67
videos.description: The Paladins shuts down the Cavaliers on the last possession to secure the upset.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Furman stuns No. 4 seed Virginia 68-67) 2023/3/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: No. 13 Furman knocks off No. 4 Virginia in wild ending
videos.description: After Virginia turns the ball over and JP Pegues hits the go-ahead 3-pointer, the Cavaliers can't convert at the buzzer and fall to Furman 68-67.
